For while she was so scared at the shelter that she preferred not to leave her kennel, but she was recently talked into a walk by a volunteer friend (who sweetened the deal with treats.) Her human pals were thrilled to see Rosa enjoying just being a dog! This girl loves to play and chase squeaky toys! Grinning from ear to ear, she bounded around the yard with her ball and laid in the sunshine. üòÑ Rosa has so many more years left of being a cheerful girl in her.
